TopicTitle: Waiter, theres a _____________ in my soup!

Articles.Content:
Hold on a minute i forgot Morty

Waiter! There's a Jebediah in my soup. I think he's making something...

Waiter, there is something sticking out of the soup, it looks white, with 3 prongs sticking out, and it shot a blue portal at the ceiling...

Edited May 1, 2016 by Planetace

Ah yes, don't look at the operational end of the device. For science.

 

Waiter, there's some *shudders* algebra in my soup.

Ooh, cool! Would you like some trigonometry on the side?

Waiter, there's a bone in my soup, looks like from a large animal.

Ah yes, we do put live pumas in our soups to give them that extra flavour.

Waiter, there's a battle going on in my soup!

Well I can sprinkle some NATO peacekeepers onto it to let the battle die down a bit. If you want a little more, I'll get the RF sprinkler. We also have a jar of Taliban, but that one doesn't really taste good, and tends to go out of control.

 

Waiter, who's head is this?

surprise!

 

waiter, there is a mario in my soup, he seems to be very sad and is crying, because the spaghetti next to me had fallen off of the table.

Nah, just ignore the environment and eat the soup.

Waiter, there's a junkyard in my soup!

wait, there is something in it:

 

waiter, there is a barrier in my soup! it seems to be trapping a small creature...

Yes... It's a squid. AND ITS PART OF THE SOUP SO YOU MUST EAT IT!!! 

Waiter! There's a b c d e f g...

(squids are fine, the kraken is not a squid nor a octopus)

well have the full alphabet, but with a part saying I   H A T E   D R E S

 

waiter! there is a dres in my soup!

@max_creative!

 

Waiter, there's an R2-D2 in my soup.

BEEP BOOP BEEP BEEP!!! 

Waiter! I am sorry to yell, because it isn't polite, but there is a C-3PO in my soup!

THIS is C-3PU

 

waiter, there is purple stuff in my soup!

Edited May 2, 2016 by Planetace

That would be me.

 

WAITER! My soup isn't herp-derping!

Yes. We got it from Eve's explodium seas, so it will g- KABOOM!!!

Waiter! There's a guy yelling "this is Sparta" in my soup!

Edit: ninja'd. 

Edited May 2, 2016 by max_creative

<Plucks guy out of soup> 

Waiter, there's a RCS thruster in my soup!

Yes, it's in your monopropellant soup. 

Waiter! There's a __________ in my soup!

Hmmm, yes, ____________!


Waiter, there's the soul-crushing realization of life's inevitability in my soup!

Just go with it.

 

Waiter, why is everyone calling on you constantly? Also, my soup just went sub-atomic!

Good, that former crazy scientist who is our chef will be fired.

Waiter, there's a Nerf Bat in my soup!

I'm sorry, we didn't realize you'd ordered the SPACE bat soup and not the Nerf bat soup! We'll make you a new one.

Soup, there's a fly in my waiter!

No, it's waiter very fly! 

Waiter there's paradox in my soup my soup my soup my soup...

We did advertise that our food will send you to a higher plane of existence, what did you expect?

 

Waiter, there's an old glove in my soup!

Joe! JOE! We have a customer complaint! Is this your glove?! You lousy damn chef!

 

Waiter! I've just found my long-lost parents!
